    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-07-09T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-07-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="24" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d24">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Sill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 25.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-07-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 9,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram of yesterday received. I told Korean minister here this
                        Government could not intervene forcibly. I did not advise him that Korea
                        should protest and notify foreign powers.</p>
            </div>
